name: The Penthouse – Two levels of indulgence await
summary: The view is always better from the top and the champagne is best sipped from a spa, as they say, or we do anyway. Step into your very own Penthouse at the head of Establishment Hotel. Two levels of indulgence await with enough room to celebrate or simply make the most of your surrounds. Entertain your entourage, have an in-room massage or we’ll sort you out with the best seat in the house at one of our many bars and restaurants
space: This 118 sqm dual-level loft on the top floor of Establishment is perfect for a weekend away or party with friends. Soaring ceilings, plenty of space, a king bed like a cloud and a bathroom bigger than a guest room, you’ll never need to leave your Penthouse suite. And, you won’t have to with room service available from Establishment and our celebrated restaurant, Mr. Wong. A Bose sound system, 50 inch Samsung TV, unlimited Netflix, and a premium mini bar also set you up for a successful stay. If you’re looking to get flexi, take advantage of our in-room yoga mats or access our private gym or get a free guest pass to Fitness First Platinum Bond Street Gym. Of course, with some of the best bars and restaurants at your doorstep, we wouldn’t fault you for stepping out on the town - and we’re happy to help you find the best seat in the house. Enjoy priority booking across all Merivale restaurants and bars, have a casual meal or a night to remember - the choice is yours.

summary: Enjoy your holiday in the heart of Manly! name: Seaside Spectacular
summary: One of the most beautiful houses in Sydney, tucked into one of her most sublime and secret bays. This is a waterfront, modernist sanctuary.
space: Shhhhhh. The Secret Gordon’s Bay Sanctuary.  While the city of Sydney rushes and screams, here is a true sanctuary. Close the gate behind you from the cul-de-sac of Gordon Ave, and wander into one of Australia’s most beautiful coastal gardens. Wattle birds, rainbow lorikeets, kookaburras and yellow tailed black cockatoos chatter from this vast garden of native plants, Sydney sandstone and ocean vistas.  Beyond the birds and trees, the Pacific Ocean stretches before you, providing a viewing platform to spot migrating whales and frolicking dolphins.  Continue down the garden path and a treasure of modernist architecture is revealed. This tiered brick house works like a theatre set, an interplay of privacy, light and space stretching across vast living areas, cosy bedrooms, quiet nooks and bathrooms which transition into rainforest. The walls of this gloriously decorated, understated house display the works of many of Australia’s finest contemporary painters. This is a luxurious house wit

neighborhood_overview: This house feels like it’s somewhere remote (you won’t hear a car or a neighbour) but it’s only a short ride from the Sydney opera house, iconic bridge, world class restaurants and entertainment venues. You can also walk to restaurants, cafes, bars, gyms, and ocean pools.
notes: There is parking for two cars in a remote controlled garage. The area is a quiet, residential area and is very private.
transit: The house is on the famous Coogee to Bondi walk (a bush track from the house takes you directly on to the path). There are buses from Coogee to Sydney city and a garage should you wish to bring your own car.
access: The entire home is available with the exception of a storage space under the house.
interaction: We will ensure someone is always available to answer your questions or see to any issues.
host_about: We are a family of five. We have used and enjoyed Airbnb in Australia, Europe and Japan. It's such a great resource and makes hotels redundant for us. We've enjoyed discovering local neighbourhoods and stepping off the tourist treadmill.

name: Huge room to rent right in front of Bondi beach
summary: Perfect location for a short term stay in Bondi. 2 minutes walk  to the beach and even a view over the ocean from the room. Bars, restaurants and shops just on the doorstep. Can be shared as a couple or as a singel. The room is huge with high ceiling and a big sunroom that is used a walk in closet.
